This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) as it deals with language models and generation strategies for text. It may also belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) as these fields are closely related to natural language processing. Additionally, it could be categorized under Neural Networks and Deep Learning (cs.NE) as these techniques are often used in language modeling. Finally, it could be categorized under Computational Linguistics (cs.CY) as it deals with the generation of natural language text.
